      "value": "<p><em>(Requires attunement by a dwarf)</em></p><p>You gain a +3 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with this magic weapon. It has the thrown property with a normal range of 20 feet and a long range of 60 feet. When you hit with a ranged attack using this weapon, it deals an extra 1d8 damage or, if the target is a giant, 2d8 damage. Immediately after the attack, the weapon flies back to your hand.</p><section class=\"secret foundry-note\" id=\"secret-DdEcPocHwtm5CFcf\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>To apply the additional damage to a giant, please use the Other Formula one more time.</p></section>",
